## Panels / Callouts

Use the `<Panel>` component for styled callout boxes:

### Warning Panel (Yellow)

```mdx
<Panel type="warning" title="Important Notice">
This feature will be deprecated in the next major release. Please migrate to the new API.
</Panel>
```

### Success Panel (Green)

```mdx
<Panel type="success" title="Good News">
Your existing integrations will continue to work without modification.
</Panel>
```

### Info Panel (Blue)

```mdx
<Panel type="info" title="Note">
This endpoint requires **API version 2.0** or higher.
</Panel>
```

### Danger Panel (Red)

```mdx
<Panel type="danger" title="Critical">
Breaking change: This update requires immediate action.
</Panel>
```

### Panel Type Reference

| Type      | Color  | Use Case                        |
| --------- | ------ | ------------------------------- |
| `warning` | Yellow | Deprecations, important notices |
| `success` | Green  | Positive news, confirmations    |
| `info`    | Blue   | Notes, additional information   |
| `danger`  | Red    | Breaking changes, critical info |

