## Styled Numbered Steps

Use the `<Steps>` component for process steps with orange circular badges:

```mdx
<Steps>
  <li>
    <strong>Create Account</strong> - Register for a developer account on the portal.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Generate API Key</strong> - Navigate to Settings and create your API credentials.
  </li>
  <li>
    <strong>Make First Request</strong> - Test your integration using the sandbox environment.
  </li>
</Steps>
```

