## Code Blocks

Use standard fenced code blocks. Add a label with a preceding span:

````mdx
<span class="code-label">JSON Response</span>

```json
{
  "status": "success",
  "data": {
    "id": "abc123",
    "name": "Example Resource"
  }
}
```
````

### Supported Languages

- `json`, `javascript`, `typescript`, `python`, `bash`, `curl`, `html`, `css`, `xml`

