## Badges

Use the `<Badge>` component for inline labels:

```mdx
<Badge type="danger">Breaking Change</Badge>
<Badge type="info">New</Badge>
<Badge type="success">Stable</Badge>
```

### Badge Types

| Type      | Color  | Use Case                    |
| --------- | ------ | --------------------------- |
| `danger`  | Red    | Breaking changes, required  |
| `info`    | Blue   | New features, informational |
| `success` | Green  | Stable, no action needed    |

