## Tables

Standard GFM tables with optional badges:

```mdx
| Parameter     | Type     | Required | Description                          |
| ------------- | -------- | -------- | ------------------------------------ |
| `api_key`     | `string` | Yes      | Your API authentication key          |
| `device_id`   | `string` | Yes      | Unique identifier for the device     |
| `callback_url`| `string` | No       | URL for webhook notifications        |
```

### Tables with Badges

```mdx
| Endpoint       | Method | Status                               |
| -------------- | ------ | ------------------------------------ |
| `/v2/devices`  | GET    | <Badge type="success">Stable</Badge> |
| `/v2/users`    | POST   | <Badge type="info">New</Badge>       |
| `/v1/legacy`   | GET    | <Badge type="danger">Deprecated</Badge> |
```

