## Images

### Standard Image

```mdx
![Alt text](/content/dam/dev-portal/your-project/image.png)
```

### Image with Caption and Lightbox

```mdx
<Image
  src="/content/dam/dev-portal/your-project/screenshot.png"
  alt="Screenshot description"
  caption="Figure 1: Dashboard overview"
  lightbox={true}
  maxWidth="600px"
/>
```

### Side-by-Side Images

```mdx
<ImageGrid>
  <Image
    src="/content/dam/dev-portal/your-project/before.png"
    alt="Before state"
    caption="Before"
    lightbox={true}
  />
  <Image
    src="/content/dam/dev-portal/your-project/after.png"
    alt="After state"
    caption="After"
    lightbox={true}
  />
</ImageGrid>
```

### Image Component Props

| Prop       | Type      | Default | Description                        |
| ---------- | --------- | ------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `src`      | `string`  | —       | Image path (required)              |
| `alt`      | `string`  | —       | Alt text for accessibility         |
| `caption`  | `string`  | —       | Caption displayed below image      |
| `lightbox` | `boolean` | `false` | Enable click-to-zoom               |
| `maxWidth` | `string`  | —       | CSS max-width (e.g., `"600px"`)    |

