## FAQ Accordions

Use the `<Accordion>` component for expandable FAQ sections:

```mdx
<Accordion id="faq1" title="How do I authenticate API requests?">
All API requests require an API key passed in the `Authorization` header.
See the [Authentication](#authentication) section for details.
</Accordion>

<Accordion id="faq2" title="What are the rate limits?">
The API allows 100 requests per minute per API key. Enterprise plans have higher limits.
</Accordion>

<Accordion id="faq3" title="How do I report a bug?">
Submit a support ticket through the developer portal or email developer-support@allegion.com.
</Accordion>
```

### Accordion Props

| Prop    | Type     | Description                           |
| ------- | -------- | ------------------------------------- |
| `id`    | `string` | Unique identifier (required)          |
| `title` | `string` | Question or heading text (required)   |

