## CSS Included

All styles are embedded in `DocLayout.astro`:

- Bootstrap base styles
- Panel styling (warning, info, success, danger)
- Styled steps with orange badges
- Code block labels
- Table styling with orange headers
- Accordion styling
- Mermaid diagram overrides
- Lightbox support

No external CSS files required.
